    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#信号与系统 #必备基础技能 #空间通信</p><h1 id="0概论"><a href="#0概论" class="headerlink" title="0概论"></a>0概论</h1><h2 id="1-信号的类别"><a href="#1-信号的类别" class="headerlink" title="1 信号的类别"></a>1 信号的类别</h2><h3 id="确定性信号与随机信号。"><a href="#确定性信号与随机信号。" class="headerlink" title="确定性信号与随机信号。"></a>确定性信号与随机信号。</h3><p>确定信号指被表述为确定的时间函数；随机信号含有许多未可预知的不确定性。一般来说，现实场景中遇到的绝大多数信号都是随机信号。</p><h3 id="周期与非周期"><a href="#周期与非周期" class="headerlink" title="周期与非周期"></a>周期与非周期</h3><p>周期较长的信号可以构成所谓“伪随机信号”，产生的伪随机码在通信系统中得到广泛应用。</p><h3 id="连续时间信号与离散时间信号"><a href="#连续时间信号与离散时间信号" class="headerlink" title="连续时间信号与离散时间信号"></a>连续时间信号与离散时间信号</h3><p>连续信号只有若干不连续点，它的幅值可以是离散的。<br>离散信号时间上是离散的，离散时间信号的时间间隔也可以是不均匀的。若离散信号的幅值是连续的，则可认为是抽样信号。</p><h3 id="一维信号与多维信号"><a href="#一维信号与多维信号" class="headerlink" title="一维信号与多维信号"></a>一维信号与多维信号</h3><p>语言信号和图像信号。</p><h3 id="常见的信号与波形"><a href="#常见的信号与波形" class="headerlink" title="常见的信号与波形"></a>常见的信号与波形</h3><h4 id="指数信号"><a href="#指数信号" class="headerlink" title="指数信号"></a>指数信号</h4><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">K</span> = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>.<span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">t</span> = -<span class="hljs-number">2</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0</span>.<span class="hljs-number">01</span>:<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">x</span> = K*exp(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>.<span class="hljs-number">6</span>*t);<br><span class="hljs-attribute">plot</span>(t,x)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20240807003830.png]]</p><h4 id="正弦信号"><a href="#正弦信号" class="headerlink" title="正弦信号"></a>正弦信号</h4><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs excel">w = <span class="hljs-number">10</span>*<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>;<br><span class="hljs-symbol">t1</span> = (<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>&gt;=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br><span class="hljs-symbol">x1</span> = K*<span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>*<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>).*<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(w*<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>);<br>figure<br>plot(<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>,<span class="hljs-symbol">x1</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20240807101718.png]]</p><h4 id="复指数信号"><a href="#复指数信号" class="headerlink" title="复指数信号"></a>复指数信号</h4><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab"><span class="hljs-comment">% 设置参数</span><br>a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">% 实数部分</span><br>b = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">% 虚数部分</span><br>t = <span class="hljs-built_in">linspace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">% 时间向量</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">% 计算复指数信号</span><br>z = <span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>((a + <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>*b) * t);<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 提取实部、虚部和幅度</span><br>realPart = <span class="hljs-built_in">real</span>(z);<br>imagPart = <span class="hljs-built_in">imag</span>(z);<br>magnitude = <span class="hljs-built_in">abs</span>(z);<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 绘图</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>;<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 实部</span><br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(t, realPart);<br>title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Real Part of e^&#123;(a+bi)t&#125;&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Time t&#x27;</span>);<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Real Part&#x27;</span>);<br>grid on;<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 虚部</span><br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(t, imagPart);<br>title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Imaginary Part of e^&#123;(a+bi)t&#125;&#x27;</span>);<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Time t&#x27;</span>);<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Imaginary Part&#x27;</span>);<br>grid on;<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 幅度</span><br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(t, magnitude);<br>title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Magnitude of e^&#123;(a+bi)t&#125;&#x27;</span>);<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Time t&#x27;</span>);<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Magnitude&#x27;</span>);<br>grid on;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>% 调整图表布局<br>sgtitle(‘Complex Exponential Signal’);<br>![[Pasted image 20240807102736.png]]</p><h4 id="抽样函数"><a href="#抽样函数" class="headerlink" title="抽样函数"></a>抽样函数</h4><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">t</span>= -<span class="hljs-number">5</span>*pi:<span class="hljs-number">1</span>/<span class="hljs-number">500</span>:<span class="hljs-number">5</span>*pi;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">x</span>=sinc(t/<span class="hljs-number">10</span>*pi);<br><span class="hljs-attribute">figure</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">plot</span>(t,x);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20240807103348.png]]</p><h4 id="钟形信号"><a href="#钟形信号" class="headerlink" title="钟形信号"></a>钟形信号</h4><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab"><span class="hljs-comment">% 设置参数</span><br>A = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">% 振幅</span><br>mu = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">% 均值</span><br>sigma = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">% 标准差</span><br>t = <span class="hljs-built_in">linspace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">-5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">% 时间向量</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">% 计算高斯钟形信号</span><br>gaussianSignal = A * <span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(-(t - mu).^<span class="hljs-number">2</span> / (<span class="hljs-number">2</span> * sigma^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>));<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 绘图</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(t, gaussianSignal);<br>title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Gaussian Bell Curve Signal&#x27;</span>);<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Time t&#x27;</span>);<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Amplitude&#x27;</span>);<br>grid on;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20240807104114.png]]</p><h2 id="2-信号的运算"><a href="#2-信号的运算" class="headerlink" title="2 信号的运算"></a>2 信号的运算</h2><h3 id="平移与反褶"><a href="#平移与反褶" class="headerlink" title="平移与反褶"></a>平移与反褶</h3><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs excel">%%<br>% clc,clear<br><span class="hljs-built_in">t</span> = linspace(-<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>); % 时间向量<br>x = (<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>&gt;=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>plot(<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>,x)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">t</span> = <span class="hljs-built_in">t</span> + <span class="hljs-number">0.5</span>;<br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br>plot(<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>,x)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">t</span> = -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>*<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>;<br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>)<br>plot(<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>,x)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20240807105509.png]]</p><h3 id="积分与微分"><a href="#积分与微分" class="headerlink" title="积分与微分"></a>积分与微分</h3><figure class="highlight lisp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs lisp">A = <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-comment">; % 振幅</span><br>f = <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-comment">; % 频率</span><br><span class="hljs-literal">t</span> = linspace(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>*pi, 1000); % 时间向量<br>x = A*sin(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*pi*f*t)<span class="hljs-comment">; % 正弦信号</span><br>dx = diff(<span class="hljs-name">x</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">; % 微分</span><br>int_x = cumsum(<span class="hljs-name">x</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">; % 积分</span><br>% 绘图<br>figure<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>plot(<span class="hljs-name">t</span>, x)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>title(&#x27;Sinusoidal Signal&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>xlabel(&#x27;Time <span class="hljs-literal">t</span>&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>ylabel(&#x27;Amplitude&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>grid on<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>plot(<span class="hljs-name">t</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:end-1</span>), dx)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>title(&#x27;Differentiation of Sinusoidal Signal&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>xlabel(&#x27;Time <span class="hljs-literal">t</span>&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>ylabel(&#x27;Amplitude&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>grid on<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>plot(<span class="hljs-name">t</span>, int_x)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>title(&#x27;Integration of Sinusoidal Signal&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>xlabel(&#x27;Time <span class="hljs-literal">t</span>&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>ylabel(&#x27;Amplitude&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>grid on<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br>sgtitle(&#x27;Differentiation and Integration of Sinusoidal Signal&#x27;)<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20240807110046.png]]</p><h2 id="3-信号的分解"><a href="#3-信号的分解" class="headerlink" title="3 信号的分解"></a>3 信号的分解</h2><p>对信号的分解有多个角度：</p><h3 id="直流分量与交流分量"><a href="#直流分量与交流分量" class="headerlink" title="直流分量与交流分量"></a>直流分量与交流分量</h3><p>![[Pasted image 20240808185413.png]]</p><h3 id="偶分量与奇分量-类比与偶函数和奇函数"><a href="#偶分量与奇分量-类比与偶函数和奇函数" class="headerlink" title="偶分量与奇分量(类比与偶函数和奇函数)"></a>偶分量与奇分量(类比与偶函数和奇函数)</h3><p>任何信号都可以分解为这两部分之和。<br>![[Pasted image 20240808185630.png]]</p><h3 id="脉冲分量"><a href="#脉冲分量" class="headerlink" title="脉冲分量"></a>脉冲分量</h3><p>将信号分解为许多脉冲分量之和：<br>1矩形窄脉冲分量；2阶跃信号分量叠加<br>![[Pasted image 20240808185845.png]]</p><h3 id="实部分量与虚部分量"><a href="#实部分量与虚部分量" class="headerlink" title="实部分量与虚部分量"></a>实部分量与虚部分量</h3><p>![[Pasted image 20240808190139.png]]</p><h3 id="正交函数分量"><a href="#正交函数分量" class="headerlink" title="正交函数分量"></a>正交函数分量</h3><p>傅里叶级数</p><h2 id="4-系统模型及其分类"><a href="#4-系统模型及其分类" class="headerlink" title="4 系统模型及其分类"></a>4 系统模型及其分类</h2><p>![[Pasted image 20240808190254.png]]<br>![[Pasted image 20240808190313.png]]<br>连续时间系统与离散时间系统。<br>即时系统与动态系统。(记忆)<br>集总参数系统与分布参数系统。<br>线性系统与非线性系统。<br>时变系统与时不变系统。<br>可逆系统与不可逆系统。</p><h2 id="5-线性时不变系统"><a href="#5-线性时不变系统" class="headerlink" title="5 线性时不变系统"></a>5 线性时不变系统</h2><p>叠加性与均匀性<br>![[Pasted image 20240808190700.png]]<br>时不变特性<br>![[Pasted image 20240808190716.png]]<br>微分特性<br>![[Pasted image 20240808190749.png]]<br>因果性(只与$t&lt;t_0$时刻的输入有关)<br>![[Pasted image 20240808190808.png]]</p><h2 id="6-本书结构"><a href="#6-本书结构" class="headerlink" title="6 本书结构"></a>6 本书结构</h2><p>![[微信图片_20240808191352 1.png]]</p><h1 id="1连续时间系统的时域分析"><a href="#1连续时间系统的时域分析" class="headerlink" title="1连续时间系统的时域分析"></a>1连续时间系统的时域分析</h1><h2 id="1-用时域经典法求解微分方程"><a href="#1-用时域经典法求解微分方程" class="headerlink" title="1 用时域经典法求解微分方程"></a>1 用时域经典法求解微分方程</h2><p>求齐次解与特解：<br>![[Pasted image 20240808191727.png]]<br>![[Pasted image 20240808191738.png]]<br>![[Pasted image 20240808192309.png]]</p><h2 id="2-起始点的跳变-0负到0正状态的转换-起始状态和初始状态"><a href="#2-起始点的跳变-0负到0正状态的转换-起始状态和初始状态" class="headerlink" title="2 起始点的跳变 0负到0正状态的转换(起始状态和初始状态)"></a>2 起始点的跳变 0负到0正状态的转换(起始状态和初始状态)</h2><p>0负：起始状态；0正：初始状态。<br>一般情况下，用时域经典法求得微分方程的解答应限于$0_+&lt;t&lt;\infty$ 的时间的范围。所以应利用0正状态作为初始条件。 </p><h2 id="3-零输入响应与零状态响应"><a href="#3-零输入响应与零状态响应" class="headerlink" title="3 零输入响应与零状态响应"></a>3 零输入响应与零状态响应</h2><p>齐次解&#x3D;自由响应；特解&#x3D;强迫响应<br>![[Pasted image 20240808194146.png]]<br>matlab求解常微分方程。</p><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs excel">dydt = @(<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>,y) - <span class="hljs-number">2</span>*y +<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>);<br><span class="hljs-symbol">y0</span> = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>tspan = [<span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span>];<br>[<span class="hljs-built_in">t</span>,y] = ode45(dydt, tspan, <span class="hljs-symbol">y0</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-冲激响应和阶跃响应"><a href="#4-冲激响应和阶跃响应" class="headerlink" title="4 冲激响应和阶跃响应"></a>4 冲激响应和阶跃响应</h2><p>以$\delta(t)$函数作为激励；称单位冲激响应；$h(t)$。<br>以$u(t)$作为激励；称单位阶跃响应；$g(t)$。<br>信号分解的一中重要方式是把待研究的信号分解为多个冲激信号&#x2F;阶跃信号的基本单元之和。</p><h2 id="5-卷积"><a href="#5-卷积" class="headerlink" title="5 卷积"></a>5 卷积</h2><p>conv。</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms r(t);<br>Dr = diff(r, t);       <span class="hljs-comment">% 一阶导数</span><br>D2r = diff(r, t, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);   <span class="hljs-comment">% 二阶导数</span><br>eq1 = D2r + <span class="hljs-number">4</span>*Dr + <span class="hljs-number">3</span>*r == dirac(t) + <span class="hljs-number">2</span>*heaviside(t);<br>y = dsolve(eq1);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">disp</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;系统的冲激响应表达式:&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">disp</span>(y)<br><span class="hljs-comment">%</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">% 定义信号 x[n] 和 h[n]</span><br>x = [<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span> <span class="hljs-number">4</span>];    <span class="hljs-comment">% 输入信号</span><br>h = [<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];      <span class="hljs-comment">% 系统冲激响应</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">% 对 x[n] 和 h[n] 进行卷积</span><br>y = conv(x, h);<br><span class="hljs-comment">% 显示卷积结果</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">disp</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;卷积结果 y[n] = conv(x[n], h[n]):&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">disp</span>(y)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>卷积若干性质：<br>1.交换律，分配律，结合律<br>2.微分与卷积<br>![[Pasted image 20240810114740.png]]<br>![[Pasted image 20240810114755.png]]<br>3.与冲激函数或阶跃函数的卷积<br>与单位冲激函数的卷积仍是本身。<br>![[Pasted image 20240810114849.png]]</p><h1 id="2傅里叶变换"><a href="#2傅里叶变换" class="headerlink" title="2傅里叶变换"></a>2傅里叶变换</h1><h2 id="周期信号的傅里叶级数分析"><a href="#周期信号的傅里叶级数分析" class="headerlink" title="周期信号的傅里叶级数分析"></a>周期信号的傅里叶级数分析</h2><p>周期函数可由三角函数的线性组合来表示。<br>![[Pasted image 20240810160803.png]]<br>![[Pasted image 20240810160815.png]]<br>并非任意周期信号都能进行傅里叶级数展开，被展开的周期函数必须满足如下的一组充分条件，即“狄里赫利条件”；<br>1 在一周期内若有间断点存在，数目应该是有限个。<br>2 极大值和极小值的数目应该是有限个。<br>3 信号是绝对可积的。<br>指数信号的傅里叶级数。<br>![[Pasted image 20240810161119.png]]<br>函数的对称性和傅里叶系数的关系：<br>偶函数的傅里叶级数不含有正弦项；<br>奇函数的傅里叶级数不含有余弦项；<br>奇谐函数只含有基波和奇次谐波的正弦、余弦项，不包含偶次谐波项。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
